lgp.core.environment.config

Interface ConfigLoader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComponentLoader<TComponent>, Module
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonConfigLoader, YamlConfigLoader

    public ConfigLoader
extends ComponentLoader<TComponent>

    An extended interface ComponentLoader that is responsible for loading class Config instances.

    The method in which the configuration is loaded is to be defined through an implementation.

    See Also:
    interface ComponentLoader, class Config, class Config
